1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:04,700
难道你不愿意孤注一掷 真刀真枪地干出点名堂
Wouldn't you rather give it all at once to something real?

2
00:00:05,370 --> 00:00:07,200
我们要偷什么
What would we be stealing?

3
00:00:07,290 --> 00:00:10,910
一整个帝国星区的季度工资
The quarterly payroll for an entire Imperial sector.

4
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:12,870
《安多》前情提要

5
00:00:12,950 --> 00:00:16,080
如果是我 我也会这样做
If I was them, this is how I'd do it.

6
00:00:16,160 --> 00:00:17,410
尽量分散
I'd spread it out.

7
00:00:18,700 --> 00:00:20,910
打一枪换一个地方
Never climb the same fence twice.

8
00:00:21,580 --> 00:00:22,580
比克丝
Bix!

9
00:00:22,660 --> 00:00:24,250
是谁干的
Who did this?

10
00:00:25,290 --> 00:00:26,250
蒂姆
Timm!

11
00:00:26,330 --> 00:00:28,160
所以你完全不抱希望是吗
So you think it's hopeless, do you?

12
00:00:28,250 --> 00:00:30,370
自由 独立
Freedom? Independence?

13
00:00:30,450 --> 00:00:32,200
我们就得逆来顺受 感激涕零
We should just submit and be thankful?

14
00:00:32,290 --> 00:00:34,500
我像感激涕零的样子吗
Do I look thankful to you?

15
00:00:35,160 --> 00:00:37,290
-下士 -听候命令
- Corporal. - At your service.

16
00:00:37,370 --> 00:00:38,700
入列
Fall in.

17
00:00:38,790 --> 00:00:39,790
向右转
Turn.

18
00:00:41,370 --> 00:00:42,200
齐步走
With me.

19
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:47,450
答应我 别出事
Tell me you'll be all right.

20
00:00:47,540 --> 00:00:48,950
放心吧
I'll be fine.

21
00:00:49,040 --> 00:00:50,370
去吧
Go.

22
00:00:52,080 --> 00:00:54,790
开始搬
Let's go!

23
00:00:54,870 --> 00:00:56,750
这是怎么回事
What is going on here?

24
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:01,750
我被困住了
I'm pinned down!

25
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:05,870
不
No!

26
00:01:05,950 --> 00:01:07,120
抓紧了
Hang on!

27
00:01:13,040 --> 00:01:16,870
我猜现在 你的前途一片暗淡吧
My assumption is, you have no prospect for the future.

28
00:01:16,950 --> 00:01:18,370
我去联系哈尔洛叔叔
I'm calling Uncle Harlo.

29
00:01:18,450 --> 00:01:19,870
好歹也是亲戚一场
I'm calling in the family favor.

30
00:01:19,950 --> 00:01:21,790
你猜里面有多少钱
You wanna guess how much is in there?

31
00:01:21,870 --> 00:01:24,450
差不多一人四千万
Forty million a piece, give or take.

32
00:01:24,540 --> 00:01:27,120
-所以你不是反抗军  -我是反抗者 不过…
-So no rebellion for you? -Oh, I'm a rebel. It's just, uh...

33
00:01:28,450 --> 00:01:29,830
我反的是所有人
me against everybody else.

34
00:01:30,700 --> 00:01:33,540
他想独吞拿笔钱 把你们都扔在这里
He wanted to take the money and leave you here.

35
00:01:33,620 --> 00:01:35,950
-他不会那么做 -我只拿走我那份
-He wouldn't do that. -I'm taking my cut.

36
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:37,080
我把事办完了
I did my job.

37
00:01:37,160 --> 00:01:39,200
我想有个人也许能帮我
I found someone I think can help me.

38
00:01:39,290 --> 00:01:40,370
我们已经岌岌可危了
We're vulnerable enough.

39
00:01:40,450 --> 00:01:42,160
我们需要资金 而不是更多人手
We need funding, not more people.

40
00:01:42,250 --> 00:01:44,540
别跟我说什么岌岌可危
Don't lecture me on vulnerability.

41
00:01:44,620 --> 00:01:46,370
没人比我冒的风险更大
No one's more at risk than I am.

42
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:44,000
《安多》
第一季第七集

43
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:44,000
本WEB版外挂字幕由  风吹来的那片云  双语合并

44
00:02:54,580 --> 00:02:55,620
希里尔
Syril?

45
00:02:57,450 --> 00:02:59,080
希里尔
Syril!

46
00:03:06,410 --> 00:03:07,700
你就打算穿成这样
Is that what you're wearing?

47
00:03:08,290 --> 00:03:09,870
就这样吧
It would seem so.

48
00:03:09,950 --> 00:03:12,120
你以为标准局会欣赏
What makes you believe the Bureau of Standards

49
00:03:12,200 --> 00:03:14,160
有个性的员工吗
is in the market for individuals?

50
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:16,000
只是件棕色衣服
It's a brown suit.

51
00:03:16,790 --> 00:03:17,910
可这是面试
It's your interview.

52
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:20,580
你是不是想和我一起去
Perhaps, you would like to come along.

53
00:03:21,660 --> 00:03:24,620
哈尔洛叔叔给你安排的 咱们可不能怠慢
Uncle Harlo's influence is not a thing to be trifled with.

54
00:03:24,700 --> 00:03:26,080
我怎么怠慢了
How am I trifling?

55
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:28,370
他这可是帮了我们一个大忙
He's done us a tremendous favor.

56
00:03:28,450 --> 00:03:31,910
你得记住 今天你不仅仅是代表自己
You need to remember you're not just representing yourself today.

57
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,330
只是件棕色衣服
It's a brown suit.

58
00:03:35,830 --> 00:03:37,040
衣领
The collar.

59
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,000
怎么了
-What about it?

60
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:39,040
太高了
-It's high.

61
00:03:39,910 --> 00:03:41,250
你把它加高了
You've had it raised.

62
00:03:41,330 --> 00:03:42,620
我定制的
I had it tailored.

63
00:03:43,370 --> 00:03:45,500
从细节能看出一切 希里尔
Everything says something, Syril.

64
00:03:45,580 --> 00:03:48,370
我想让你明白 你总是不听
I've tried to make you understand that, you've resisted.

65
00:03:49,290 --> 00:03:51,040
你从我的衣领能看出什么
What is it that you hear my collar saying?

66
00:03:52,500 --> 00:03:53,660
"看看我"
"Look at me.

67
00:03:54,750 --> 00:03:56,410
"我对自己没信心"
"I don't believe in myself.

68
00:03:56,500 --> 00:03:58,750
"我迫切需要认可"
"I am desperate for approval."

69
00:03:58,830 --> 00:04:00,500
我们刚刚收到令人震惊的报告
We have distressing reports are reaching us

70
00:04:00,580 --> 00:04:02,790
阿尔达尼的帝国军械库
that a terror attack and robbery

71
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:06,040
遭到恐怖袭击和抢劫
have taken place at the Imperial Armory on Aldhani,

72
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:08,500
据报道有多人死亡
with multiple fatalities reported.

73
00:04:08,580 --> 00:04:09,660
怎么回事
What happened?

74
00:04:09,750 --> 00:04:11,660
-暴徒 -发布了封锁令…
- Rabble. - ...a Blockade Order was issued...

75
00:04:11,750 --> 00:04:12,870
他们袭击了当地驻军
They attacked a garrison.

76
00:04:12,950 --> 00:04:14,330
他们会后悔的
They'll regret it.

77
00:04:14,410 --> 00:04:16,950
现场官员仍在评估损失
...officials on the scene are still assessing the loss

78
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,830
并搜寻共谋者
and searching for the conspirators.

79
00:04:19,450 --> 00:04:23,160
昨晚袭击阿尔达尼的罪犯
The criminals responsible for last night's atrocity on Aldhani

80
00:04:23,250 --> 00:04:25,790
自认为打得帝国措手不及
think they've taken the Empire by surprise.

81
00:04:26,250 --> 00:04:27,450
我们早有准备
We know better.

82
00:04:27,540 --> 00:04:29,830
他们将在震惊中发现
We know the real shock will be

83
00:04:29,910 --> 00:04:34,870
我们随时可以积极回应
when they discover how ready and eager we are to respond,

84
00:04:34,950 --> 00:04:37,910
今天上午我们在这里
to be prepared, to be here this morning

85
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,370
需要讨论的唯一问题
and know that the only question

86
00:04:39,450 --> 00:04:44,200
就是打击手段的强硬程度
we need to answer is how tight to close our fist.

87
00:04:45,250 --> 00:04:46,790
所以我们要制定计划
This is why we plan.

88
00:04:46,870 --> 00:04:50,700
要在和平时期居安思危
This is why we work so hard when we're at peace.

89
00:04:50,790 --> 00:04:56,540
所以我们招募人员如此严格 要求如此之高
This is why we recruit so carefully and demand so much.

90
00:04:56,620 --> 00:05:01,620
从今天起 帝国全境将采取以下措施
The following measures will be adopted Empire-wide as of today.

91
00:05:02,370 --> 00:05:07,330
任何窝藏叛军的地区都将加征税款
A tribute tax equal to five times the amount stolen from Aldhani

92
00:05:07,410 --> 00:05:11,120
金额相当于阿尔达尼劫案的五倍
will be levied on any sector harboring partisan activity.

93
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:16,250
我们将昭告天下 没人能盗窃帝国财产
We will make it clear that no one steals from the Empire.

94
00:05:16,330 --> 00:05:23,250
任何利用地方习俗 传统节日或民族文化 掩护叛军行动的地区
The use of any local custom, festival, or tradition as cover for rebel activity

95
00:05:24,660 --> 00:05:29,160
将被帝国永久撤销民俗许可
will trigger permanent revocation of Imperial tolerance.

96
00:05:30,870 --> 00:05:33,540
昨晚我觐见了帕尔帕廷皇帝
I spoke with Emperor Palpatine last night,

97
00:05:35,080 --> 00:05:41,540
他向我保证 帝安局将全面主导相关工作
and he's assured me that the ISB will be taking the lead going forward.

98
00:05:41,620 --> 00:05:43,160
在座各位
No one in this room

99
00:05:43,250 --> 00:05:47,080
都将有权调用陆海军的任何资源
should have trouble accessing Army or Naval resources in future.

100
00:05:48,830 --> 00:05:52,450
皇帝将召开议会紧急会议
The Emperor will be convening an emergency session of the Senate

101
00:05:52,540 --> 00:05:55,910
提出一揽子法案和修正案
to propose a legislation package of bills and amendments

102
00:05:56,000 --> 00:06:01,750
全面放开我们的权限 进行监视 搜查和扣押
that will free our hands in all matters of surveillance, search, and seizure.

103
00:06:02,540 --> 00:06:07,580
我们将在今天晚些时候 援引公共秩序重判指令
We will be invoking the Public Order Resentencing Directive later today.

104
00:06:07,660 --> 00:06:10,410
公序重判令
P-O-R-D.

105
00:06:10,500 --> 00:06:16,000
任何犯罪行为 包括对帝国产生间接损害
Any criminal act, with even indirect effect on the Empire,

106
00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:19,790
今后都将被列为一级犯罪
will henceforth be branded a Class One Offense.

107
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:24,620
所有刑期将立即重新评估
All prison sentences are immediately re-evaluated.

108
00:06:24,700 --> 00:06:28,580
所有未缴罚款和征费都将全额支付
All outstanding fines and levies are to be paid in full.

109
00:06:28,660 --> 00:06:30,910
-我已向皇帝保证… -你不太高兴
- I have assured the Emperor... - You're not pleased.

110
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:34,000
这种做法正中他们下怀
We're playing straight into their hands.

111
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,830
-他们是谁  -叛军
- Whose hands? - The rebels.

112
00:06:37,790 --> 00:06:39,330
这正是他们想要的
This is exactly what they want.

113
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,620
把阿尔达尼事件仅仅当作一次抢劫
We're treating what happened at Aldhani like a robbery.

114
00:06:42,700 --> 00:06:44,200
那您怎么看
What would you call it?

115
00:06:45,790 --> 00:06:46,950
这是一次宣言
An announcement.

116
00:06:47,540 --> 00:06:51,250
初步调查显示 损失超过八千万信用点
Preliminary investigation puts the loss

117
00:06:51,330 --> 00:06:54,290
驻防基地所有军事人员都已被替换
at over eighty million credits.

118
00:06:51,330 --> 00:06:54,290
All military personnel at the garrison have been replaced

119
00:06:54,370 --> 00:06:56,660
正在接受帝安局审查
and are being interrogated by ISB.

120
00:06:56,750 --> 00:06:58,660
帝安局证实逃跑飞船上的跟踪装置
ISB confirms the tracking devices

121
00:06:58,750 --> 00:07:02,250
在到达超空间之前就已遭到破坏
in the escape craft were disabled prior to it reaching hyperspace.

122
00:07:02,330 --> 00:07:06,040
134名阿尔达尼居民已被拘留
134 Aldhani residents have been taken into custody

123
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:08,290
他们涉嫌教唆恐怖分子
under suspicion of abetting the terrorists.

124
00:07:13,450 --> 00:07:14,660
蒙·莫思马
Mon Mothma.

125
00:07:16,330 --> 00:07:17,410
她怎么来了
Without warning?

126
00:07:18,250 --> 00:07:19,790
收起你的笑容
Wipe the smile off your face.

127
00:07:30,250 --> 00:07:31,500
我应该提前通知你
I should've called.

128
00:07:31,580 --> 00:07:34,950
我们正在去议会的路上 突然想起会路过这里
We're on our way to the Senate, I realized we'd be passing by.

129
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,500
-等我一会 -好的
- I'll be right back. - Ma'am.

130
00:07:37,870 --> 00:07:40,200
佩林说他喜欢 不知道是不是真心话
Perrin likes it, I'm just not sure he loves it.

131
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:42,870
我还是换另外那个吧
I think I might want the other one.

132
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,160
你干的吗
Was this you?

133
00:07:52,250 --> 00:07:53,580
什么意思
What do you mean?

134
00:07:53,660 --> 00:07:55,330
阿尔达尼的驻防基地
The garrison. Aldhani.

135
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:57,450
那是真的
Ah! Is it true?

136
00:07:57,540 --> 00:07:59,330
克蕾娅刚和我说…
Kleya was just...

137
00:08:02,290 --> 00:08:04,910
我一直担心你会做这种事
I've been worried you might do something like this.

138
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,580
我真希望是我
How I wish I had.

139
00:08:08,290 --> 00:08:09,500
先来看看吧
Let's have a look.

140
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,500
我不相信你
I don't believe you.

141
00:08:16,580 --> 00:08:19,200
-说明你不够努力 -别这样跟我说话
-Well, you'll have to try harder. -Don't you dare talk to me like that.

142
00:08:19,290 --> 00:08:21,200
革命是需要代价的
Revolutions are expensive.

143
00:08:21,290 --> 00:08:23,040
我告诉过你 我已经竭尽全力了
I told you, I'm doing everything I can.

144
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:25,870
你的"全力"似乎只是
Your "everything" seemed to be all about

145
00:08:25,950 --> 00:08:28,620
找一个救星来取用你的家庭资金
bringing in a savior to access your family funds.

146
00:08:31,910 --> 00:08:33,120
是你干的 对吗
It was you, wasn't it?

147
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:39,330
我向你解释过找外人的风险 但你似乎不以为然
I explained to you the risk of new faces, but you seemed to know better.

148
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,660
你知道你做了什么吗
You realize what you've done?

149
00:08:43,330 --> 00:08:46,410
我以为你是来说会议的事
I thought you were here to tell me about the meeting.

150
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:47,540
是今晚
It's tonight.

151
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,410
他们可能会改期
They may reschedule.

152
00:08:53,540 --> 00:08:55,120
一开始我就警告过你
I warned you when we started.

153
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:58,370
-你说我们在建立一个网络 -我当时是怎么说的
-You told me we were building a network. -What were my words?

154
00:08:58,450 --> 00:09:00,080
这完全是另一回事
This is something else entirely.

155
00:09:00,160 --> 00:09:01,750
"一旦开始就不可能回头"
"Turning back will be impossible."

156
00:09:02,410 --> 00:09:04,250
你知道事情会怎么发展
You knew where this was going.

157
00:09:04,330 --> 00:09:05,410
你心里很清楚
You've always known.

158
00:09:10,660 --> 00:09:13,040
谁会制造武器却只当摆设
Has anyone ever made a weapon that wasn't used?

159
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:17,250
网络已经建成 开始运作
The network's been built. It's up.

160
00:09:19,250 --> 00:09:20,750
不进则退
It grows or it dies.

161
00:09:21,950 --> 00:09:23,540
我们已经等得够久了
We've waited long enough.

162
00:09:23,620 --> 00:09:26,200
你明白这会导致什么后果吗
You realize what you've set in motion?

163
00:09:26,290 --> 00:09:27,540
是时候面对后果了
It was time for that as well.

164
00:09:27,620 --> 00:09:29,700
-帕尔帕廷现在不会犹豫了 -没错
-Palpatine won't hesitate now. -Exactly!

165
00:09:30,700 --> 00:09:31,660
正如我们所愿
We need it.

166
00:09:32,790 --> 00:09:33,830
我们需要恐惧
We need the fear.

167
00:09:34,870 --> 00:09:36,290
需要他们反应过度
-We need them to overreact.

168
00:09:36,370 --> 00:09:37,580
你说什么疯话
-You can't be serious.

169
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:42,450
帝国在慢慢扼住我们的喉咙 而我们在渐渐麻木
The Empire has been choking us so slowly, we're starting not to notice.

170
00:09:43,370 --> 00:09:45,330
是时候逼他们下狠手了
The time has come to force their hand.

171
00:09:45,410 --> 00:09:46,830
人民会受苦
People will suffer.

172
00:09:48,750 --> 00:09:50,040
这是计划的一部分
That's the plan.

173
00:09:51,870 --> 00:09:53,160
你并不生我的气
You're not angry at me.

174
00:09:54,290 --> 00:09:56,410
我只是大声说出你已经知道的事情
I'm just saying out loud what you already know.

175
00:09:57,370 --> 00:09:59,330
接下来将不会有任何规则
There will be no rules going forward.

176
00:10:00,290 --> 00:10:02,250
如果你狠不下心
If you're not willing to risk your conscience,

177
00:10:02,330 --> 00:10:04,200
那就投降放弃吧
then surrender and be done with it.

178
00:10:10,160 --> 00:10:12,450
我们要竭尽所能搞到每一笔钱
We need every credit we can get our hands on.

179
00:10:13,700 --> 00:10:15,370
记得告诉我会议进展
Let me know how the meeting goes.

180
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:23,000
恐怕今天早上这两样我都不想要
I'm afraid I won't be taking either of these pieces this morning.

181
00:10:24,620 --> 00:10:27,660
我这里很快会到一批新货
